ActCanada National Parks Act
SubjectWapusk National Park of Canada Park Use Regulations
PrecisWAPUSK NATIONAL PARK OF CANADA PARK USE REGULATIONS, in order to implement the terms of the Federal - Provincial Memorandum of Agreement for Wapusk National Park concluded in 1996 between the Government of Canada and the Government of Manitoba, and to provide a framework for the control of traditional renewable resource harvesting in the park.
